# Code Quality Checks

<rule>
name: code_quality_checks
description: On any code change, the `nvm use && .dxcli/dxcli.sh quality` command line must be executed and pass successfully.
filters:
  - type: event
    pattern: ".*"  # Match any event
  - type: file_extension
    pattern: ".*"  # Match any file extension
actions:
  - type: execute
    command: "nvm use && .dxcli/dxcli.sh quality"
    require_success: true
    message: "All code quality checks (formatting, linting, type checking) must pass before merging."
</rule>

